{"tid":1137093,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"【逃犯條例】批評李家超月內見政黨商界 9 次 記協邀會晤被拒表遺憾","createTime":"2019-05-03T13:14:32.000Z","updateTime":"2019-05-03T15:01:23.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":2,"replies":[{"pid":"02171a379000e30686d57739270b1f7765fa8436","tid":1137093,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T13:14:32.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A7%E8%A6%8B%E6%94%BF%E9%BB%A8%E5%95%86%E7%95%8C-9-%E6%AC%A1-%E8%A8%98%E5%8D%94%E9%82%80%E6%9C%83%E6%99%A4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%BA%E6%86%BE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A9%2595%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%2595%2586%25E7%2595%258C-9-%25E6%25AC%25A1-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E5%258D%2594%25E9%2582%2580%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2599%25A4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E9%2581%25BA%25E6%2586%25BE%2F&d=piXtWL8Gd%2FER6BG70pbW95uyGkzLGvEkvhYecc72uXM%3D&h=15d62b21\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.thestandnews.com%2Fpolitics%2F%25E9%2580%2583%25E7%258A%25AF%25E6%25A2%259D%25E4%25BE%258B-%25E6%2589%25B9%25E8%25A9%2595%25E6%259D%258E%25E5%25AE%25B6%25E8%25B6%2585%25E6%259C%2588%25E5%2585%25A7%25E8%25A6%258B%25E6%2594%25BF%25E9%25BB%25A8%25E5%2595%2586%25E7%2595%258C-9-%25E6%25AC%25A1-%25E8%25A8%2598%25E5%258D%2594%25E9%2582%2580%25E6%259C%2583%25E6%2599%25A4%25E8%25A2%25AB%25E6%258B%2592%25E8%25A1%25A8%25E9%2581%25BA%25E6%2586%25BE%2F&h=a66960aa\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.thestandnews.com/politics/%E9%80%83%E7%8A%AF%E6%A2%9D%E4%BE%8B-%E6%89%B9%E8%A9%95%E6%9D%8E%E5%AE%B6%E8%B6%85%E6%9C%88%E5%85%A7%E8%A6%8B%E6%94%BF%E9%BB%A8%E5%95%86%E7%95%8C-9-%E6%AC%A1-%E8%A8%98%E5%8D%94%E9%82%80%E6%9C%83%E6%99%A4%E8%A2%AB%E6%8B%92%E8%A1%A8%E9%81%BA%E6%86%BE/</a><br />\n<br />\n立場報道<br />\n【逃犯條例】批評李家超月內見政黨商界 9 次 記協邀會晤被拒表遺憾<br />\n<br />\n2019/5/3 &mdash; 17:39<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/58659956_10161526540010265_263119179840749568_n_2PuwW_1200x0.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F58659956_10161526540010265_263119179840749568_n_2PuwW_1200x0.png&h=10263fb3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n李家超<br />\n<br />\n香港記者協會早前已聯同多個傳媒工會及機構，致函保安局局長李家超，要求會面商討業傳媒界感憂慮的《逃犯條例》修訂。記協指保安局日前回覆，指局長未能抽空會面，記協表示對李家超一方面積極與商界代表會面，卻未能抽空與傳媒業界會面表示遺憾。<br />\n<br />\n保安局的覆函指，局長因忙於協助立法會審議草案，亦預期立法會法案委員會將會頻密地召開會議，因此局長及其團隊未能抽空與傳媒業界會面。<br />\n<br />\n保安局的覆函又指，「條例中的所有人權和程序保障，均得以保留。」<br />\n<br />\n記協指，李家超就《逃犯條例》修訂事宜，近月穿梭與最少 9 個政黨及商會收集意見和「解畫」，卻不理記協訴求，「我們理解局長公務繁忙，未能親身與傳媒工會及組織會面，倘保安局整個團隊也無法派出一個代表與傳媒工會及組織會面，實難免令人覺得局方漠視傳媒行業的訴求。」根據記協的統計，自今年 2 月 13 日開始，李家超先後和 5 個政黨及 4 個商會或商界代表會面，解釋《逃犯條例】<br />\n<br />\n記協指，《逃犯條例》修訂不單對商界或對傳媒行業有所響，對整個香港的市民影響深遠，「我們憂慮，一旦修例落實，現時香港僅餘的言論、出版及新聞自由空間，將嚴重倒退，記者因憂慮人身安全，面對無形無盡的心理壓力，亦將造成寒蟬效應。」<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.thestandnews.com/media/photos/cache/58978444_10156998827660309_8469463783004176384_n_BKEnM_1200x0.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.thestandnews.com%2Fmedia%2Fphotos%2Fcache%2F58978444_10156998827660309_8469463783004176384_n_BKEnM_1200x0.jpg&h=dfd63ebb&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n圖片來源：香港記者協會"},{"pid":"07acdd0d83a9ccf7777d398cb5271bd773fa2121","tid":1137093,"uid":50457,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-05-03T15:01:23.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />淨係見共狗"}]}